messages.messageBody:
One of the girl's (of the preacher from TX) boyfriend died in a car accident
and so they went home. Boy they sure were unorganized. Must be hard when
you have so many different people coming together with different ideas. I
can't imagine they came into it not realizing they would have to work their
butts off all day long every day, though. Interesting to watch people.

Angela

messages.subject: colonial house
messages.msgSnippet: My favorite list has been VERY quiet lately! Ben and I just finished watching PBS Colonial House. At the end, we saw that Coldwell Banker was a sponsor. Ben
messages.messageBody:
My favorite list has been VERY quiet lately!

Ben and I just finished watching PBS' Colonial House.

At the end, we saw that Coldwell Banker was a sponsor. Ben thought that that
was a bit ironic. <g>

I added that to make it worse, they could have added Lowe's, a grocery store
(Piggly Wiggly was my suggestion), Time-Warner Cable, and Microsoft! <G>

Anybody else watch?

~Kelly
